## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date information and the inherent variability in the application of martial law across different jurisdictions. Additionally, the legal interpretations of martial law can vary, leading to differing opinions on its implementation and consequences. Historical accounts may also be subject to bias, depending on the sources and perspectives of the authors.